from or designed for use with code which is subject to the terms of the 
Apache License version 2.0 (the "License").</p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt">Copyright 2010 ARM</p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt">The
